09/10/2009
BELGRADE, Serbia -- Police have arrested five people in connection with a homemade bomb that was lobbed at the popular Belgrade-based television channel, RTV Pink, Interior Minister Ivica Dacic announced on Thursday (October 8th).
The five were detained during operations in Belgrade and Nis.
Police say the attack, late Saturday, stemmed from a quarrel with the TV channel's security personnel.
The bomb caused minor damage but no injuries.
(Tanjug, B92, Beta, Politika - 08/10/09)
